column5: well there isn't enough ice to fish on does anyone want to help me drag my folding boat across the ice at willow beach and slide it into the open water for whitefish . . . . .
I know that spot in the picture, that can't possibly be a recent shot.
LOL, no it is quite frozen over there....I was just showing the boat that needs dragging out
So Terry, how you going to get the boat back onto the ice  Be careful if you do go out please.  We have a date this weekend remember, I don't want to be stood up  Joey
Something tells me,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,NO THANKS LOL  You wouldnt dare,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,would he ?????????????????????? NNAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA  He,s just fool,n us. LOL
i may be new to this country bud but i know enough to know thats a bad idea remember play safe folks
haha.... yeah a real bad idea  oh wait it was my idea  and no I didn't dig my boat out and try..I just really want to fish for them
